es White）是来自纽芬兰圣约翰斯的加拿大电影和电视演员。","name":"珀西·海因斯·怀特","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"IL","iso_639_1":"he","name":"עִבְרִית","english_name":"Hebrew","data":{"biography":"","name":"פרסי היינס וייט","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"UA","iso_639_1":"uk","name":"Український","english_name":"Ukrainian","data":{"biography":"","name":"Персі Гайнс Вайт","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"HK","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"波西·海恩斯·懷特（Percy Hynes White）是來自紐芬蘭聖約翰斯的加拿大電影和電視演員。","name":"波西·海恩斯·懷特","primary":false}}]}},"person_2433584_translations":{"at":1773688734880,"data":{"id":2433584,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"","name":"Tania Lentini","primary":true}}]}},"person_93331_translations":{"at":1773688737169,"data":{"id":93331,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"RU","iso_639_1":"ru","name":"Pусский","english_name":"Russian","data":{"biography":"","name":"Дмитрий Назаров","primary":true}},{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"","name":"Dmitri Nazarov","primary":false}}]}},"person_2982907_translations":{"at":1773688737772,"data":{"id":2982907,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"","name":"Zakhar Vykvytke","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"RU","iso_639_1":"ru","name":"Pусский","english_name":"Russian","data":{"biography":"","name":"Zakhar Vykvytke","primary":true}}]}}}}